text: Novyye Kartavly () is a rural locality (a village) in Alkinsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 364 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Maloyaz, 7 km from Alkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Novyye Kartavly
